data.description: THIS SPACIOUS RANCH HOME IN FOUNTAIN PLACE SUBDIVISION IS IN THE O'FALLON SCHOOL DISTRICT! You will love the open floor plan & split bedroom concept. This turn-key home has been well maintained & is ready for a new owner! The eat-in kitchen offers a butterfly island, plenty of cabinet/countertop space, tile backsplash & pantry. The breakfast nook opens to the fenced in backyard which also has a nice sized patio area, perfect for grilling or entertaining. The master bedroom has a vaulted ceiling & a large walk-in closet. The master bath features dual sinks, a soaking tub & separate shower. There are two other ample sized bedrooms on the opposite side of the home, as well as another full bath. Other features include main level laundry, two car garage & a basement that would be perfect to add additional square footage in the future or for storage. Community pool, stocked pond, walking trail, soccer fields & more! Convenient location to interstate, restaurants, shopping & Scott AFB!
